metadata.name: Emoji Fight Club #1
metadata.description: Welcome to Emoji Fight Club! The first rule of Emoji Fight Club is: you do talk about Emoji Fight Club. The second rule of Emoji Fight Club is: you DO talk about Emoji Fight Club! Third rule of Emoji Fight Club: if someone yells 'stop!', goes limp, or taps out, the fight is over. Fourth rule: only two emojis to a fight. Fifth rule: one fight at a time, fellas. Sixth rule: the fights are bare knuckle card battle, best of 5 each round, high card wins. No shirt, no shoes, no weapons. Seventh rule: fights will go on as long as they have to. And the eighth and final rule: if you have an Emoji Fight Club NFT, you have to fight. Emoji Fight Club NFTs are a collection of 5,555 generated and unique pieces. Each Emoji Fight Club NFT is 100% unique and is programmatically generated from 70+ traits.
